<div class="fullDetails">
	<p>Thinner, faster and lighter than before, the Surface 2 is a petite but powerful tablet that can do more. Coming complete with Office 2013 RT (including Outlook), a micro SD card reader for up to 64GB extra storage and a crystal clear 1080p Full HD widescreen display, the Surface 2 has all you need.</p><ul><li>Includes free Skype for a year enabling you to stay in touch with friends and family all over the world. For more information and availability please see www.skype.com/surface.</li><li>Also features an extra 200GBs of SkyDrive Storage free for two years. For further information and availability, please see www.skydrive.com/surface.</li><li>Keyboard purchased separately.</li></ul><p>Display:</p><ul><li>10.6 inch screen.</li><li>Resolution 1920 x 1080 pixels.</li><li>Multi-touch screen.</li></ul><p>Specifications:</p><ul><li>1.7GHz quad core NVIDIA - Tegra 4 Quad-core processor.</li><li>2GB RAM.</li><li>32 GB internal storage.</li><li>Windows 8 RT operating system.</li></ul><p>General features:</p><ul><li>Built-in speaker.</li><li>Webcam.</li><li>Wi-Fi enabled.</li><li>Bluetooth - enabling you to easily and wirelessly connect with other bluetooth enabled devices.</li><li>3.5mm stereo headphone jack.</li><li>Microphone.</li><li>microSD memory card slot.</li><li>1 x USB 3.0.</li><li>HDMI.</li></ul><p>Additional information:</p><ul><li>Up to 10 hours battery life (depending on usage).</li><li>8mm thin.</li><li>Size H17.3, W27.5cm.</li><li>Weight 675g.</li><li>EAN: 885370620498.</li></ul>
